title: India's Fluffiest Omelet Making | Super Fluffy Omelet | Indian Street Food
description:
WOW Omelette's is a popular street food place in Hyderabad serving the most unique and super fluffy omelet. The making of this omelet is very interesting and satisfying to watch. First, they whip the eggs till it gets foamy or bubbly, then they fry it on pan with butter on low heat. Then they flip it very carefully to cook the other site, the final result is a super fluffy omelet. 



Address : WOW Omelette's (Inspired By Chef. Sanjay Thumma), 35, IDL LAKE, Habeeb Nagar, Kukatpally, Hyderabad, Telangana
